4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp, which allows individuals to become cybersecurity specialists even without prior knowledge. The program covers topics such as Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Participants will also learn about data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. The bootcamp lasts for 16 weeks, with 3 live online classes per week and a maximum class size of 16 people. Upon completion, participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop